caption.center: MARISA ABERNATHY AND KEVIN BURRIS, Appellants, v. BLAKRISHNA NAVAS

court.center: Court of Appeals of Texas, Fifth District, Dallas.

opinion.posture:
On Appeal from the County Court at Law No. 4, Dallas County, Texas, Trial Court Cause No. CC-05-09823-D.
Dismiss.
opinion.panel: Before Justices BRIDGES, FITZGERALD, and LANG.
opinion.opinion_text: The Court has received appellee's notice of settlement. In the notice, which indicates appellant's counsel's agreement, appellee states the parties have come to a compromised settlement in the matter. Accordingly, we dismiss the appeal. See Tex.R.App.P. 42.1(a)(2).
